com.smartthings.sdk.smartapp.core.extensions.contextstore

Class DefaultInstalledAppContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartthings.sdk.smartapp.core.extensions.contextstore.DefaultInstalledAppContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstalledAppContext

    public class DefaultInstalledAppContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements InstalledAppContext
    This is the default implementation of InstalledAppContext which stores basic information related to installed apps. In particular, this includes token information to allow for keeping them up-to-date for out of band API requests. Instances of this class are created and managed by the context store.
